data.description:
Bed-Stuy Dream! Renovated-Updated-Move-In-Mid-Block, stunning turn of the century 2-family, 3-story brownstone located in the heart of historic Bedford-Stuyvesant. This amazing property has three livable floors and a cellar making it an excellent income-generating property or a wonderful multi-generational home. Bed-Stuy is a highly sought after neighborhood, a popular food scene and home to every type and style of cuisine with coffee houses, bars & cafes, shopping, beautiful parks, 8 subway trains, bus lines, numerous bike lanes and just 15-20 minute commute to Manhattan! Being sold unoccupied!
Proof of Funds or Pre-Approval required for an appointment.
